# mcp-sql-rust — Core

Binary: `mcp-sql-rust`. Crate: `mcp_sql_rust`. Repo: https://github.com/rzlco666/mcp-sql-rust

## Stack

Rust + Tokio + `rmcp` + `sqlx` (PG/MySQL) + `sqlparser` + `clap` + `dotenvy`.

## Locked decisions (do not silently change)

1. Default tool surface = **3 tools** (`search_objects`, `execute_sql`, `analyze_query_performance`)
2. Extra tools only behind `--full-tools`
3. Write policy tiers: ReadOnly → AllowWrites → AllowDdl
4. Result format = **columnar JSON only**
5. Guard runs **before** pool checkout on deny
6. Transports: stdio + Streamable HTTP (`--http`)

## Module map

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/main.rs` | clap + tracing + transport select |
| `src/config.rs` | .env walk, TOML sources, WriteMode |
| `src/db/` | pool, exec, explain, schema |
| `src/guard/` | AST classify + enforce |
| `src/format/` | columnar serializer |
| `src/tools/` | MCP tool handlers |
| `src/server.rs` | rmcp router + HTTP |

